messageBody:
Hi Ritesh,



Thanks for your reply but I was using that book. I needed
some other book which tells more along with good number of examples.

If I find such book I would surely inform the group.



Regards,

Sreedevi.

Hi All,



I am a new member to this group, new to work with Junit And new for
testing also.

Can anyone suggest me good books or documents which have many examples
of testcases, testsuites.

And please suggest me, what more things do I need to understand about
junit as a beginner.



Regards,

Sreedevi.
